text: Kelly Anderson (born 4 February 1983) is a New Zealand cricketer. She played in six Women's One Day International cricket (WODI) matches and two Women's Twenty20 International cricket (WT20I) matches in 2011. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand women cricketers Category:New Zealand women One Day International cricketers Category:New Zealand women Twenty20 International cricketers Category:Cricketers from Auckland
